rows.label: qst620104_msg0001
rows.name: Hello-lo! Bipopo ho-ome!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0002
rows.name:
Ah, useless sonnypon finally decide
to grace home with presence?

rows.label: qst620104_msg0003
rows.name: Mehmeh?

rows.label: qst620104_msg0004
rows.name:
Wait, are you Melolo's son,
Bipopo?

rows.label: qst620104_msg0005
rows.name: Yes!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0006
rows.name:
Melolo hesitate to admit it,
but yes.

rows.label: qst620104_msg0007
rows.name:
Usually sonnypon sit around, play
board game all day, no help at all
around house!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0008
rows.name:
So Melolo very proud when sonnypon
say he leave to find work in Gula.
But why home so soon?

rows.label: qst620104_msg0009
rows.name:
Bipopo tell mamapon, but must
listen to story before angry.

rows.label: qst620104_msg0010
rows.name: Meh?

rows.label: qst620104_msg0011
rows.name:
Mamapon give Bipopo money 
for get set up in Gula...
But money all gone.

rows.label: qst620104_msg0012
rows.name: Gone?!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0013
rows.name:
You mean you get robbed?
And Rex here save my Bipopo?!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0014
rows.name:
A-ah... Yes.
That exactly what happen.

rows.label: qst620104_msg0015
rows.name: Er, that's not quite how it went.

rows.label: qst620104_msg0016
rows.name:
Bipopo spend all money on
famous game called Tiger! Tiger!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0017
rows.name: MEH? What this?!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0018
rows.name:
Sorry to ask mamapon when 
look so shocked, but Bipopo
needing another 50,000G.

rows.label: qst620104_msg0019
rows.name: This time definitely find work!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0020
rows.name:
Say find work, but clearly plan to
waste all on game again! Mamapon
not born yesterday!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0021
rows.name:
Melolo not give any money!
Not in million years!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0022
rows.name:
And useless sonnypon no more
sonnypon of mine!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0023
rows.name: No want see Bipopo ever again!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0024
rows.name: Mehmeh?!
軽く暗転入れて三人で相談

rows.label: qst620104_msg0101
rows.name: Meh... *Sniffle*

rows.label: qst620104_msg0102
rows.name: Erm...

rows.label: qst620104_msg0103
rows.name:
What Bipopo do now? 
Come back to Gula?

rows.label: qst620104_msg0104
rows.name: Bipopo want...

rows.label: qst620104_msg0105
rows.name:
OH! Bipopo remember! Brought
gift for Mamapon in case of
bad situation!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0106
rows.name: The Tank Mod III!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0107
rows.name:
Ah, yeah! That's the prize you
got from Tiger! Tiger!, right?

Melolo and Bipopo are talking.
Tora and Rex watch from a 
distance.

rows.label: qst620104_msg0201
rows.name:
Mamapon, Bipopo pick this up
for you in Gula.

rows.label: qst620104_msg0202
rows.name: What that?

rows.label: qst620104_msg0203
rows.name:
Is called Tank Mod III. In Gula, 
very popular, very valuable!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0204
rows.name:
Mamapon like salvage things, so
Bipopo want give, but...

rows.label: qst620104_msg0205
rows.name: Bipopo is...

rows.label: qst620104_msg0206
rows.name: Bipopo is best useless sonnypon!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0207
rows.name: Mamapon so happy!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0208
rows.name:
Bipopo hopeless good-for-nothing
sonnypon, but always welcome at
home with Mamapon.

rows.label: qst620104_msg0209
rows.name: Thank you, Mamapon!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0210
rows.name:
Hooray! Even Tora feeling
moved!

rows.label: qst620104_msg0211
rows.name:
All's well that ends well...
I suppose.
